⍝ Catenate.tc
⍝ ═══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A and B conformable arrays
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ,⌈/(⍴⍴A),(⍴⍴B),1
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      Z ← A,B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,⌈/(⍴⍴A),(⍴⍴B),1
1
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z) ←→ (¯1↓⍴A),(¯1↑⍴A)+(¯1↑⍴B)   same-rank arrays
      (⍴Z) ≡ (¯1↓⍴A),(¯1↑⍴A)+(¯1↑⍴B)
1
      ⍝ inv: (¯1↓⍴A) ←→ ¯1↓⍴B   (conformability)
      (¯1↓⍴A) ≡ ¯1↓⍴B
1
